Attributes:

  * `progress-bar` {`boolean`} - True if a progress bar is shown instead of dots.

Use a progress bar when there are many steps, or if there are
steps that need to be inserted during the process (based o
responses to earlier steps).

  * `back-label` {`string`} - Text for the back button. Use this property to localize the element.

  * `next-label` {`string`} - Text for the back button. Use this property to localize the element.

  * `disable-previous` {`boolean`} - Boolean for disabling the previous button.

  * `disable-next` {`boolean`} - Boolean for disabling the next button.

  * `no-buttons` {`boolean`} - Hide back/next buttons
